text:
I was trying to get my
   passport and the visa, but I never got the chance to get the visa because I
   heard a lot of rumors saying that people that are trying to get visas from
   here, from Mexico, most of the time they reject them and not give them to
   them, so I was like, I don't want to waste my money, because the visa here
   costs 4,000, almost 5,000 to get the visa.
name: Yair
